title: CLEAR_GPS_DISABLED_ZONE_AT_INDEX

0x2801D0012266DF070x59090745// ClearGpsDisabledZoneAtIndex
void CLEAR_GPS_DISABLED_ZONE_AT_INDEX(int index);Parameters:index: Index of disabled zone.Clears a disabled GPS route area from a certain index previously set using SET_GPS_DISABLED_ZONE_AT_INDEX.Old name:  _CLEAR_GPS_DISABLED_ZONE_AT_INDEX
